trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of component-related commands, which have predefined key input gestures and <see cref="P:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text" /> properties.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce un set standard di comandi correlati al componente, che hanno movimenti di input chiave e proprietà <see cref="P:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text" /> predefinite.

trans-unit.source: The commands in the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: I comandi di <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> classe e i comandi in altro comando classi della libreria, ad esempio <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> e <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, rappresentano un set di comandi comuni che i programmatori di applicazioni incontrano frequentemente.

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: I comandi rappresentano solo l'istanza del <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> e non la logica di implementazione per il comando.

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command via a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: La logica di implementazione è associata al comando tramite un <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command is executed on a control (the command target), the logic that performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> command may not be provided by the command target, so the application writer is responsible for writing the logic that determines how the command target handles the command.
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, se il <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> comando viene eseguito su un controllo (destinazione del comando), la logica che esegue il <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands.MoveLeft%2A> comando potrebbe non essere fornito per la destinazione del comando, pertanto il writer dell'applicazione è responsabile della scrittura logica che determina come la destinazione del comando gestisce il comando.

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic, though, for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: Molti controlli fornire la logica di implementazione, tuttavia, per molti dei comandi nella libreria del comando.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> command, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> command, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> command.
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> classe fornisce la logica per il <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A> comando <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A> comando <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A> comando, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A> comando, e <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> comando.

trans-unit.source: See the class documentation for particular control classes for more information.
trans-unit.target: Vedere la documentazione di classe per le classi di controllo specifico per altre informazioni.

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni sui comandi e l'esecuzione di comandi, vedere [panoramica dei comandi](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).
